ind
***

‘ind’ displays the current date in a variety of civil, historical,
religious, astronomical, regnal, and idiosyncratic systems.

   This manual explains the principal calendars, cycles, observances,
and continuous day counts represented in the display.  For the command
itself, type ‘M-x ind’.

